  "text": "MBM is a widely used technique for the ER of neoplasia in the esophagus. MBM is effective in selected groups of patients [CITATION_1] and it allows safe piecemeal resections in patients with BE neoplasia. Time and costs are saved compared with the cap and snare technique [CITATION_2] .",
